<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
    <title>Neuer Kurstermin</title>

    <style>
        @import url("https://use.typekit.net/dcz3wfu.css");
        @import url("https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.1.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css");
        h1,h2,h3,h4,h5,h6{
            font-family: aw-conqueror-didot, serif!important;
            line-height: 1!important;
            font-weight: 400!important;
        }
        p,a{
            font-family: sofia-pro, sans-serif!important;
            line-height: 1.6!important;
            font-weight: 300!important;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body class="m-0 p-0">
<div class="bg-warning">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-12">
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

<div class="pt-5 bg-warning">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="col-12">
            <div class="card rounded-0 border-0">
                <div class="card-body mt-3">
                    <div class="row">
                        <div class="col-12 text-center">
                            <h1>Hi {{ user.firstName }}!</h1>
                            <img src="https://cdn.cinekolleg.de/images/icons/icons8_google_alerts_96px.png" class="mt-3" width="96" height="96" alt="handshake">
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="pb-5 bg-light">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="col-12">
            <div class="card rounded-0 border-0">
                <div class="card-body">
                    <div class="row">
                        <div class="col-12 text-center">
                            <p>
                                Für den Kurs <span class="fw-bold">{{ course.course.title }}</span> gibt es einen weiteren Termin:
                            </p>
                            <p class="lead">
                                {{ course.date|date('d.m.Y') }}, um {{ course.time|date('H:i') }} Uhr<br>
                                <b>Ort:</b> {{ course.location }}
                            </p>
                            <p><b>Thema:</b> {{ course.subject }}</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="row">
                        <div class="col-12 text-center">
                            <a class="btn btn-warning rounded-0 px-5 my-4" href="{{ url('tutorium_show',{id:course.course.id}) }}">Zum Kurs</a>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="row">
                        <div class="col-12">
                            <p>Sollte das nicht funktionieren, kopiere bitte den Link in die Browserzeile:</p>
                            <p class="link-primary">{{ url('tutorium_show',{id:course.course.id}) }}</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="row g-3">
                        <div class="col-12">
                            <p>Mit lichtmalerischen Grüßen<br/>
                                <img src="https://cdn.cinekolleg.de/images/graphics/sign.png"  alt="sign"><br>
                                Benjamin Wagner</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>
</div>

<footer class="pt-2 bg-dark" id="about">
    <div class="container pt-5">
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-12">
                <div class="hero mb-3">
                    <img src="https://cdn.cinekolleg.de/images/logo/logo.png" alt="logo" height="96"><br>
                    <a href="https://www.cinekolleg.de" class="link-light small">https://www.cinekolleg.de</a>
                </div>
                <div class="text-white d-flex flex-column mb-3 small">
                    <p>
                        Wagner Pictures<br>
                        Postfach 96 11 19<br>
                        12474 Berlin
                    </p>
                    <p>
                        049/554/01625
                    </p>
                    <span>&copy;2022 Wagner Pictures</span>
                    <a href="https://www.wagnerpictures.com" class="link-light small">https://www.wagnerpictures.com</a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</footer>
</body>
</html>
